When I write content, I always like to bring some negative things into it. Maybe some people have misunderstood my intentions and dislike me.
Bring some negative things into the topic does not represent negative energy, because I think there is a contrast between negative and positive, that can reflect that negative things are wrong, and then there are opportunities for improvement. Only you can see the wrong self from the negative. Negative things basically exist, why are you afraid to bring them up? Perhaps you use the credit or contribution of others to become your own achievement, or get big praise and more applause even if you know it is obviously wrong, but this is an dishonour.
Be sure you put your feet in the right place, then stand firm.
